provenance:
  derived_from: [asyncio source, Python docs, https://docs.python.org/3/library/asyncio-sync.html, https://docs.python.org/3/library/asyncio-task.html]
  not_derived_from: [asyncio_extra2866.zspec.zsdl — covers __rand__/__ror__/__rxor__ dict-presence, asyncio_extra2851.zspec.zsdl — covers __rlshift__/__rrshift__/__rpow__ dict-presence, asyncio_extra2836.zspec.zsdl — covers __rtruediv__/__rfloordiv__/__rmod__ dict-presence]
  notes: [Wave 639 theme — __iadd__/__isub__/__imul__ dict-presence checks for asyncio types. In-place augmented assignment operators. Task/Future/Queue/Event/Semaphore/BoundedSemaphore/Lock/Condition/Handle/TimerHandle/Timeout/TaskGroup are async coordination primitives not numeric/sequence types — none define these dunders. All expected values verified with Python 3.14.4 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0 2026-04-13.]
  created_at: "2026-04-13"

